member.remarks:
You can use this struct like this:

foreach (short mask in new BitSubsetsGenerator(9, 3))
{
    // Do something to use the mask.
}

remarks.para:
In some case, you can use object initializer instead.
You can use the code

var map = new Cells { 0, 3, 5 };

instead of the code

var map = new Cells(stackalloc[] { 0, 3, 5 });

In some case, you can use object initializer instead.
You can use the code

var map = new Cells { 0, 3, 5 };

instead of the code

var map = new Cells(stackalloc[] { 0, 3, 5 });

For example, if the offset is -2 (~1), the [1] will be assigned :

var map = new Cells(xxx) { ~1 };

which is equivalent to:

var map = new Cells(xxx);
map[1] = false;

