remarks.para:
This enumeration type is called to select what the inner field we want to fix. For example,
if called  (parameterless method), the default value is
, and we'll get the table that contains all current statuses of the
current grid using a *. The code should be:

fixed (short* s = grid)
{
    // Do something...
}

The code is equivalent to

fixed (short* s = &grid.GetPinnableReference())
{
    // Do something...
}

summary.para:
For example, if you want to get the name of the size 3, the code will be

string name = TechniqueStrings.SubsetNames[3];

Here the digit 3 is the size you want to get.

For example, if you want to get the name of the size 3, the code will be

string name = TechniqueStrings.RegularWingNames[3];

Here the digit 3 is the size you want to get.
